description:
Progress of Reform in Germany: After the Diet of Worms Martin Luther would disappear from the public eye, spending time in Wartburg Castle and spent time translating the Bible into German amongst other things. This was a crucial time for the Reformation in Germany with several situations that could have derailed the movement.
